reviewText:
Expected, when labelled Volume 4, that it would carry on from the end of dvd series 3.  Not the case.  Disappointed.
The story was magnificent and can hardly wait for the dvd series to continue.  This vhs offering is not it.

i would love to see the final two  in the series. but to no avail. only vhs is available, why would you say the complete set when two  are missing, false advertising i would say.  cmon, lets have these two in dvd.
